luating investment returns oversee investment expenses analyzing nontraditional investments institute prudent procedures establish investment “best practices” our firm’s experience is deep broad and practical cca acts not only as an advisor but also as an independent fiduciary decision maker when the fund’s regular fiduciaries require additional support and management   we know — and deliver to our clients — investment “best practices” bizapediacom  human validation companiespeopleproductsservicestrademarksaddressesphone book our system has detected a high number of page requests from your ip address please prove to us that you are a human to continue using our website please send me to the search subscription offer page after i successfully answer the word challenge bizapediapro searchperform unlimited searches via ouradvanced search form withbizapedia pro searchfind out more bizapediapro databuild custom data listsfor one or many stateswith bizapedia pro datafind out more  copyright   · bizapediacom · all rights reservedblogpro searchpro apicontact usterms of useprivacy policysitemapdesktop version cca investments trust llc  cca aggressive return fund private company information  bloomberg july    am et capital markets company overview of cca investments trust llc  cca aggressive return fund snapshot people company overview cca investments trust llc  cca aggressive return fund is an open ended balanced mutual fund launched and managed by checchi capital fund advisers llc the fund is comanaged by checchi capital advisers llc it invests in public equity and fixed income markets of the united states for its equity portion the fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors it invests in stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations with a focus on smallcap companies having market capitalization of  million or more for its fixed income portion the fund invests in securities which are rated ccc or higher by sp or caa or higher by moody’s and of any maturity cca investments trust llc  cca aggressive return fund is an open ended balanced mutual fund launched and managed by checchi capital fund advisers llc the fund is comanaged by checchi capital advisers llc it invests in public equity and fixed income markets of the united states for its equity portion the fund invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors it invests in stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations with a focus on smallcap companies having market capitalization of  million or more for its fixed income portion the fund invests in securities which are rated ccc or higher by sp or caa or higher by moody’s and of any maturity it seeks to benchmark the performance of its portfolio against the composite benchmark consisting of barclays global aggregate bond index msci usa imi index msci eafe imi index msci emerging markets imi index and a composite benchmark index consisting of  barclays global aggregate bond index  msci us investable market index  msci eafe investable market index and  msci emerging markets investable market index the fund employs proprietary research to create its portfolio cca investments trust llc  caa aggressive return fund was formed on september   and is domiciled in the united states detailed description  north canon drivesuite beverly hills ca united statesfounded in  phone  fax  key executives for cca investments trust llc  cca aggressive return fund mr adam dean checchi portfolio manager dr sam pfister phd portfolio manager compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global m